OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry at first with some bright
OL,6,Fspells, mostly inthe east. Quickly
OL,7,Fturning increasingly cloudy and windy
OL,8,Finto the afternoon with the odd spot
OL,9,Fof rain. Mild in the brighter spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStorm Dave will bring strong
OL,12,Fwinds this evening with some heavy and
OL,13,Fblustery spells of rain at times. The
OL,14,Fstorm will clear in the early hours
OL,15,Fand winds will ease.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,18,Fshowers on Easter Day with lighter
OL,19,Fwinds. Feeling colder than previous
OL,20,Fdays with a fresh breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
